short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension extends the basic Youtube Hotkeys to give the user more functionality.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With TubingKeys, you get extra Hotkeys that help you browse through Youtube.

A = Go back 5 Seconds
S = Play/Pause
D = Go Forward 5 Seconds
